<p>I have a matlab code that include some function handle in simple form like:</p>  <pre><code>Cx=@(x,landa1) sin(landa1*x)-sinh(landa1*x); Cy=@(y,landa2) cos(landa2*y)-cosh(landa2*y); </code></pre>  <p>now i want to construct function handle that in mathematical form is product of <code>Cx</code> and <code>Cy</code> but it is necessary for my code that this new function handle construct base on two existing function of <code>Cx</code> and <code>Cy</code> and any solution such as:</p>  <pre><code>Cxy=@(x,landa1,y,landa2) (sin(landa1*x)-sinh(landa1*x))*(cos(landa2*y)-cosh(landa2*y)); </code></pre>  <p>are not acceptable.</p>